text: Chiyoko stayed up late, didn't she...!

Sorry...! I just got carried away
wanting to perfect everything...!

That's the spirit! But remember,
overdoing it is a no-no, okay?

I know it goes without saying that
if I miss tomorrow's lesson, it's all over...

No need to worry!
I appreciate your concern!

Yes! I feel like I'm gradually
mastering new things, little by little...

It's so much fun competing and striving
to catch up and surpass everyone!

So, as long as it doesn't affect tomorrow,
I'm planning to try out a few more things...
